{UTF-8}
Cumulative LED Energy Used= INTEG (Energy Draw Rate,
		0)
	~	kWh
	~		|

Energy Draw Rate=LED Intensity * 50
	~	kWh/Day
	~		|

LED Intensity=1
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Nutrient Injection Rate=Plant Transpiration * (1 - Water Recycling Efficiency)
	~	Liters/Day
	~		|

Nutrient Water Reservoir= INTEG (Nutrient Injection Rate-Plant Transpiration,
		1000)
	~	Liters
	~		|

Photosynthetic Growth Rate=(Vertical Crop Biomass * 0.1) * LED Intensity
	~	kg/Day
	~		|

Plant Transpiration=Vertical Crop Biomass * 0.05
	~	Liters/Day
	~		|

Vertical Crop Biomass= INTEG (Photosynthetic Growth Rate,
		10)
	~	kg
	~		|

Water Recycling Efficiency=0.95
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 90
	~	Day
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Day
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP 
	~	Day [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 1
	~	Day [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

